divs: Sighting DetailsLooking at the the night sky at approx. 9:15 pm in the SE direwction just to the right of a big star. The light would move in all directions, separate into pieces and then come back together. The object stayed for a long time, over 30 minutes. There seemed to be more than opne of these objects, moving very rapidly in all directions. I could see the planes going to LAX airport undermneath the UFO.
